{"word":"G276 - ἀμετάθετος - ametáthetos - am-et-ath'-et-os - Immutable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμετάθετος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ametáthetos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am-et-ath'-et-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Immutable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மாறாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not transposed, not to be transferred; fixed, unalterable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3346 - μετατίθημι - metatíthēmi - met-at-ith'-ay-mee/3346\">G3346</a>; <i>unchangeable</i>, or (neuter as abstract) <i>unchangeability:</i> - immutable (-ility).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}